1. Return Jonathan's Twitter handle (i.e. the string "jonnyt")
users["Jonathan"][:twitter]


2. Return Erik's hometown
users["Erik"][:home_town]


3. Return the array of Erik's favorite numbers
users["Erik"][:favourite_numbers]


4. Return the type of Avril's pet Colin
users["Avril"][:pets]["colin"]


5. Return the smallest of Erik's favourite numbers
users["Erik"][:favourite_numbers].min 


6. Return an array of Avrils favourite numbers that are even
array_favourite_numbers = users["Avril"][:favourite_numbers]
  for numbers in array_favourite_numbers
    puts numbers if numbers.to_f%2 == 0
  end


7. Return an array of Jonathans favourite numbers, sorted in ascending order and excluding duplicates
users["Jonathan"][:favourite_numbers].sort.uniq


8. Add the number 7 to Erik's favorite numbers
users["Erik"][:favourite_numbers].push(7)


9. Change Erik's hometown to Edinburgh
users["Erik"][:home_town] = "Edinburgh"




